sentences.sentence: Then I went to see Late Night Gimp Fight.
sentences.translation: 所以，我就去看了《深夜打架的瘸子》。

sentences.sentence: The pitch of Late Night Gimp Fight is simple.
sentences.translation: 《深夜打架的瘸子》意图很简单。

sentences.sentence: There are also some to fix common problems of GIMP.
sentences.translation: 还有其他一些是修复GIMP的普通问题的。
